OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776971469
OL,3,C'No relief' for heating oil customers
OL,4,Cuntil Middle East war is resolved
OL,6,FHome heating oil customers in Northern
OL,7,FIreland will see no relief from high
OL,8,Fprices until the conflict in the
OL,9,FMiddle East is resolved, MPs have been
OL,10,Ftold.
OL,12,FDavid Blevings, executive director of
OL,13,Fthe Northern Ireland Oil Federation
OL,14,Fsaid the war had had a "devastating
OL,15,Feffect" on the industry.
OL,17,FThe Northern Ireland Affairs Committee
OL,18,Fheard evidence from industry
OL,19,Frepresentatives about the rise in
OL,20,Fenergy prices.
OL,26,@vD@XOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
