FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776971469
OL,3,C'No relief' for heating oil customers
OL,4,Cuntil Middle East war is resolved
OL,6,FThe cost of fuel has soared since the
OL,7,Fwar in Iran.
OL,9,FThe US and Israel began bombing Iran
OL,10,Fon February 28, after which the
OL,11,FIranians began an effective blockade
OL,12,Fof vital trading route the Strait of
OL,13,FHormuz, disrupting energy and fuel
OL,14,Fsupplies.
OL,16,FIn Northern Ireland, almost two thirds
OL,17,Fof domestic properties use home
OL,18,Fheating oil.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776971469
OL,3,C'No relief' for heating oil customers
OL,4,Cuntil Middle East war is resolved
OL,6,FMr Blevings said the situation in the
OL,7,FMiddle East had had a "huge impact,
OL,8,Fnot only on my industry, but on
OL,9,Fconsumers".
OL,11,FHe added: "We have seen a huge spike,
OL,12,F97% in the price of kerosene locally
OL,13,Fand again that is due to the factors
OL,14,Fof the American invasion of Iran and
OL,15,Fthe closure of the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,17,F"It has had a huge impact on my
OL,18,Fmembers getting product and obviously
OL,19,Fthe price they have to pay for that
OL,20,Fproduct.
OL,26,@oD@WOUqD@JO]sD@KOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776971469
OL,3,C'No relief' for heating oil customers
OL,4,Cuntil Middle East war is resolved
OL,6,F"We have seen a huge amount of panic
OL,7,Fbuying by consumers and no matter how
OL,8,Fmany times you tell people not to
OL,9,Fpanic buy, it usually has the opposite
OL,10,Feffect.
OL,12,F"It has had a devastating effect on
OL,13,Fthe industry itself and a fear factor,
OL,14,FI think, for consumers thinking ahead
OL,15,Fto this winter."
OL,17,FHe added: "Until the situation is
OL,18,Fresolved in the Middle East we are not
OL,19,Fgoing to see any short-term relief.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@PO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776971469
OL,3,C'No relief' for heating oil customers
OL,4,Cuntil Middle East war is resolved
OL,6,F"If the Strait of Hormuz remains
OL,7,Fclosed I do worry about the future for
OL,8,Fthis winter.
OL,10,F"We have about 40% of jet fuel which
OL,11,Fcomes from the Gulf states, if it is
OL,12,Fresolved quickly in the next couple of
OL,13,Fweeks we could see a return to
OL,14,Frelative normality by quarter four of
OL,15,F2026.
OL,17,F"But if we have a prolonged infraction
OL,18,Fin Iran this winter in particular
OL,19,Flooks very difficult."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
