PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776971469
OL,3,C'No relief' for heating oil customers
OL,4,Cuntil Middle East war is resolved
OL,6,FLast week the Stormont Executive
OL,7,Fannounced a relief scheme which will
OL,8,Fallow home heating oil customers with
OL,9,Fan income of less than #30,000 to
OL,10,Fapply for a #100 prepaid card.
OL,12,FMr Blevings said: "#100 won't even buy
OL,13,Fyou 100 litres in today's terms. Can
OL,14,Fwe not look at removing the 5% VAT?
OL,16,F"That is relatively simple to do and
OL,17,Fwould be effective for consumers who
OL,18,Fearn over the #30,000.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776971469
OL,3,C'No relief' for heating oil customers
OL,4,Cuntil Middle East war is resolved
OL,6,F"I have had a lot of calls from people
OL,7,Fwho earn #32, #33, #34,000, they are
OL,8,Fsaying they are going to miss out on
OL,9,Fthis #100."
OL,11,FHe added: "I would have concerns about
OL,12,Fthis winter if we don't (see) a
OL,13,Fresolution to this problem in the
OL,14,FMiddle East in the next two to three
OL,15,Fweeks."
OL,17,FThe committee also heard from William
OL,18,FIrvine, the president of the Ulster
OL,19,FFarmers' Union.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]sD@KOUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776971469
OL,3,C'No relief' for heating oil customers
OL,4,Cuntil Middle East war is resolved
OL,6,FHe said Northern Ireland's agri-food
OL,7,Fsector is facing an "immediate and
OL,8,Fexternally driven cost shock".
OL,10,FMr Irvine said: "This has put the
OL,11,Fstress on farms to a new level.
OL,13,F"Our intensive sector are quite high
OL,14,Fenergy users, we are on the point of
OL,15,Four grass harvest season which
OL,16,Frequires a lot of fuel.
OL,18,F"Our arable and potato guys are
OL,19,Fparticularly vulnerable.
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@]O]rD@QOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1776971469
OL,3,C'No relief' for heating oil customers
OL,4,Cuntil Middle East war is resolved
OL,6,F"We are hearing reports of potato
OL,7,Ffarmers selling their harvest
OL,8,Fmachinery to raise the capital to
OL,9,Fplant this year's crop.
OL,11,F"How that is sustainable I do not know
OL,12,Fbut that is the pressure that is at
OL,13,Ffarm level at the moment."
